                <img src="images/people/dashboard-monitor.svg" alt="Dashboard Icon" loading="lazy">
                <aside>
                    <h3>Details of Staff Dashboard</h3>
                </aside>
                <p>The Staff Dashboard serves as your central workspace within the Sacred Harvesters
                International Christian School Dashboard. From here, you can view your personal information,
                monitor your attendance history, and manage your daily academic responsibilities.
                The dashboard is designed to be simple and user-friendly, ensuring that you can
                focus more on teaching and less on administrative processes. All data displayed
                here is securely managed and updated by the school administration.</p>
                <button class="close-dialog" id="close-dialogbox" aria-label="Close Dialog Box">Close</button>
            </dialog>
        </aside>
        <aside  class="aside animation">
            <img src="images/people/to-do.svg" alt="Dashboard Icon" loading="lazy">
            <h2>What you can Do</h2>
            <p>
            As a staff member, you can easily view your attendance records, upload lesson
            notes, and stay informed about your work history within the school. The system
            ensures that your attendance is accurately recorded by the administration,
            promoting transparency and accountability.
            </p>
            <button class="open-dialog" id="open-whatToDo">Learn More -></button>
            <!--DIALOG BOX SECTION-->
            <dialog class="dialog-box my-dialog" id="whattodo-dialogbox" aria-labelledby="dialog-label" aria-describedby="dialog-desc">
            <aside>
                <h3>What you can Do</h3>
