            allowing the school to keep a well-organized academic archive. By using this system,
            you contribute to a more efficient workflow and better communication between staff
            and school management.</p>
            <button class="close-dialog" id="close-WhatToDo" aria-label="Close Dialog Box">Close</button>
        </aside>
        <aside class="aside animation">
            <img src="images/people/hr-person.svg" alt="Dashboard Icon" loading="lazy">
            <h2>Encouragement</h2>
